{"tid":2337002,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"廠機換顯示卡求解","createTime":"2020-12-23T04:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T13:40:58.000Z","uid":189879,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d57bd8f723462b01ea55171433e397ef53324517","tid":2337002,"uid":189879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"今朝打打下機個mon無啦啦黑咗,但見主機仲著住燈<br />\n於是熄主機總掣重開機,個畫面就變咗咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWAg1Tj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWAg1Tj.jpg&h=3dc17347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個mon見唔到mouse cursor,鍵盤撳咩制都冇反應<br />\n<br />\n上網search咗一輪估計係顯示卡出問題<br />\n所以目前打算換張GeForce GT 1030<br />\n但見佢要嘅Watt數係300W<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2M178yL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2M178yL.png&h=4ff1891e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而依家我用緊嘅火牛得180W (依家先知得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtqMEF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtqMEF7.jpg&h=6ea86bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣係咪火牛都要一齊換埋?<br />\n<br />\n再加上我見依家個火牛嘅size同出面大多數都唔同<br />\n換火牛嘅話係咪連埋機箱一齊換?<br />\n懇求大家幫忙解答一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係主機內部<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WOemtCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWOemtCf.jpg&h=a80de220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢個係廠機Spec<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUHWhvd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUHWhvd.png&h=f4404b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LyRQQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LyRQQe.png&h=0b08f848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係電腦白癡,如果有錯麻煩大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a556ce37922a8e273a93c1cf20b87801c23ecf14","tid":2337002,"uid":157358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"你部機本身張gt730都 38w tdp啦 30w咪仲少<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f1ce2a5cf5acc3cd9ce10b830b0680864f1e2e","tid":2337002,"uid":229100,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"買過部算啦 牛又要換 卡又要換 底板又唔一定岩用"},{"pid":"25725c049f31fe217a0b3c7b963751d06d849ca9","tid":2337002,"uid":50423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"爛novo咁仆街, 配粒f版u<br />\n9代u配古董gt730開機卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nf版u又冇onboard display<br />\nbtw 但你有畫面應該唔係壞display<br />\n同埋你打咩機 730都打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ff5ca2012a50ccd659e90c42692f41d74dae36","tid":2337002,"uid":5475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"換個部算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫黎嘥藥費"},{"pid":"f2ea1544be0ef6933517d02e1276e740d7ec5fc2","tid":2337002,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"[XF] 入門裝機新選擇 MSI GT 730 2GB DDR3 開箱測試<br />\nTsaik Tsaik &middot; 2014-10-06 <br />\n<br />\n處理器編號 i5-9400F<br />\n推出日期 Q1'19<br />\n<br />\n2019 u 配 2014年display card<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f85eba71854bf9585a5687eb42c1e5dfdf3399","tid":2337002,"uid":50423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"btw 部機咁新應該未過保, 應該可以call main搞<br />\n上爛novo個網打s/n可check保養期"},{"pid":"ce26e510dfde87581dbb1da69271d89acdd2f519","tid":2337002,"uid":244137,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"電腦白痴都搵到咁多野先上來問, 比個like你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1030定位就係廠機卡, 基本上直上冇問題<br />\n廠機有保養既最好打去搵原廠先"},{"pid":"4bbc22d7c179a97e0aaf8b816dc1fc7b52a71bbf","tid":2337002,"uid":47999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"度好機箱尺吋<br />\n<br />\n小心新買既1030塞唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddc81afa601f0c8868c4ed5f116206cc87b4c64","tid":2337002,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"應該同display card冇關<br />\n開機去到登入畫面應該正常?<br />\n試下安全模式做下diagnostic先"},{"pid":"1a90b5923f7b2ec260941f0c51a2f1993b30495b","tid":2337002,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"end of support 2025-10-30，係咪仲有保啊？"},{"pid":"af625237635691c3b94dad04b9b9b8aab9dabe4e","tid":2337002,"uid":189879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25725c049f31fe217a0b3c7b963751d06d849ca9","tid":2337002,"uid":50423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"爛novo咁仆街, 配粒f版u<br />\n9代u配古董gt730開機卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nf版u又冇onboard display<br />\nbtw 但你有畫面應該唔係壞display<br />\n同埋你打咩機 730都打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"玩緊隻休閒Game Train Valley,FPS突然間由60急降到10幾,心諗唔對路,跟住就黑咗mon<br />\n另外s/n嗰邊已經搵到了,唔該曬巴打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7NOThY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7NOThY.png&h=46973327&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ddd3f55022d49fb9badf3d0bc010eee6b9f81f6","tid":2337002,"uid":189879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ddc81afa601f0c8868c4ed5f116206cc87b4c64","tid":2337002,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"應該同display card冇關<br />\n開機去到登入畫面應該正常?<br />\n試下安全模式做下diagnostic先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"成個登入畫面卡咗喺度冇反應,所以應該開唔到安全模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4336acfa2a12c7abd33cb38d73c5bce9420e78ff","tid":2337002,"uid":189879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a90b5923f7b2ec260941f0c51a2f1993b30495b","tid":2337002,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"end of support 2025-10-30，係咪仲有保啊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"啱啱搵到了,唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc4c767b000c55e47db6422abf4da53b7f98415","tid":2337002,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"唔一定要砌過部嘅，文書機用得就用，自已DIY升級電腦係一種樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼見嘅問題同建議<br />\n(1) 牛火數太細，加張1030 我估最少上個3,400W，不過睇隻廠牛似啤死喺機箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇下拆唔拆到出黎<br />\n<br />\n(2) 機箱風扇數量唔夠，板上面有冇兩個4-PIN頭? <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ekwb.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/01-1-1030x638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ekwb.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F01-1-1030x638.jpg&h=1651799b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機箱前後有冇各4個相隔12CM的螺絲窿? 有就平平地買再把風扇仔頭尾裝一把<br />\n<br />\n(3) ram槽在HDD下面? check下ram，拆隻HDD出黎用擦子膠擦幾下條ram金屬片部位再安裝返上去 (最好順手吸下啲千年塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n(4) 有冇CD-ROM位? 有一種5.25&quot;層架可以上螺絲的，咁你就可以裝隻SSD再戰十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005c4a073f0295c631f94b1f45bf1eb01545b208","tid":2337002,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"730仲未停產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedb3dcda079565c258908e76bdd568a98867cd2","tid":2337002,"uid":173121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"冇救 ，砌多部算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963810b7c45fbd74cc3c2c7b7746af862b3eb8fd","tid":2337002,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多,買牛同卡不如成部換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}